Federation of Labor (HISTADRUT) unless Arab rights were restored
and the Mideast peace is achieved," he said.
</P>
<P>
Egypt established diplomatic relations with Israel in 1979, but
most of its professional unions have not normalized ties with the
Jewish state because of lack of progress in the Mideast peace
process. 
